Package: solrium
Title: General Purpose R Interface to 'Solr'
Description: Provides a set of functions for querying and parsing data
    from 'Solr' 'endpoints' (local and remote), including search, 'faceting',
    'highlighting', 'stats', and 'more like this'. In addition, some
    functionality is included for creating, deleting, and updating
    documents in a 'Solr' 'database'.
Version: 0.2.8.9550
